燃「燭」治文書", "皆汝「肩」之", "輒以手批「頰」數四", "侍者「為」之悚慄"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-106-chinese-passage-45", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "97fdb0fabe32", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0fa526cf1539", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 45, "raw_text": "45. 「佟中丞鳳彩巡撫河南」句中「巡撫」二字\n                        \n    的詞性，與下列何者相同？        1.矍然：驚視貌。矍，音ㄐㄩㄝˊ\n    (A)燃「燭」治文書\n    (B)皆汝「肩」之\n    (C)輒以手批「頰」數四\n    (D)侍者「為」之悚慄\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-106-chinese-046", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-106-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文的敘述，可推知佟中丞的為人如何？", "options": ["自許甚高，治事嚴謹", "嫉惡如仇，律下嚴厲", "貧賤不移，威武不屈", "豁達大度，不拘小節"], "correct_answer": 0, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-106-chinese-passage-45", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "97fdb0fabe32", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0fa526cf1539", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 46, "raw_text": "46.   根據本文的敘述，可推知佟中丞的為人如何？\n      (A)自許甚高，治事嚴謹\n      (B)嫉惡如仇，律下嚴厲\n      (C)貧賤不移，威武不屈\n      (D)豁達大度，不拘小節\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-106-chinese-047", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-106-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "關於這兩首詩的內容，下列敘述何者正確？\n", "options": ["甲詩描寫時間為晚上，乙詩描寫時間是清晨    1.扶桑：相傳東海外有神木名", "甲詩送別地點在扶桑，乙詩分別地點在揚子江        為扶桑，是日出之", "甲詩作者將與友人同行，乙詩作者送友人獨往        地。亦為日本別名", "甲詩友人以船為交通工具，乙詩友人亦是如此"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-106-chinese-passage-47", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "97fdb0fabe32", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0fa526cf1539", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 47, "raw_text": "47.   關於這兩首詩的內容，下列敘述何者正確？\n                                \n      (A)甲詩描寫時間為晚上，乙詩描寫時間是清晨    1.扶桑：相傳東海外有神木名\n      (B)甲詩送別地點在扶桑，乙詩分別地點在揚子江        為扶桑，是日出之\n      (C)甲詩作者將與友人同行，乙詩作者送友人獨往        地。亦為日本別名\n      (D)甲詩友人以船為交通工具，乙詩友人亦是如此\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-106-chinese-048", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-106-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "關於這兩首詩的寫作手法，下列敘述何者正確？", "options": ["甲乙兩詩皆遲至末句才點出友人前行的目的地", "甲乙兩詩各自重複某些字詞，增添詩的節奏感", "甲詩由眼前景寫到想像景，乙詩從想像景寫到眼前景", "甲詩只有二、四句用韻，乙詩是一、二、四句皆用韻 13               試題結束"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-106-chinese-passage-47", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "97fdb0fabe32", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0fa526cf1539", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 48, "raw_text": "48.   關於這兩首詩的寫作手法，下列敘述何者正確？\n      (A)甲乙兩詩皆遲至末句才點出友人前行的目的地\n      (B)甲乙兩詩各自重複某些字詞，增添詩的節奏感\n      (C)甲詩由眼前景寫到想像景，乙詩從想像景寫到眼前景\n      (D)甲詩只有二、四句用韻，乙詩是一、二、四句皆用韻\n\n                      13               試題結束\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}]'::jsonb) AS t(
